author: Joshua Nelson
title: Cotton claims China's leaders decided to let rest of the world suffer from coronavirus
description: Sen. Tom Cotton, R-Ark., claimed on “Outnumbered Overtime" Thursday that China's leaders made a "deliberate” decision to allow the coronavirus to spread around the world.
